{"tid":521893,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺巴塞同皇馬個板凳深度好似幾個月內倒轉左咁","createTime":"2018-01-07T04:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-07T22:39:16.000Z","uid":18279,"like":62,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9ebd850fef6cc3666188710e6cce07a1a49a3022","tid":521893,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"之前巴塞個陣<br />\n<br />\n尼馬 蘇狗 美斯<br />\n小白 影帝 拉傑迪<br />\n艾巴 碧基 黑人 羅白<br />\n達子<br />\n<br />\n前場無替補可言，得個艾卡沙，中場後備無個合格，右閘更加長期缺人，只有左閘、龍門、中堅叫夠人。依家變陣選擇多左好多，前場尼馬換個丹比利、艾卡沙同屌老虎都叫做華西隊長同a米主力，古天奴又可翼可攻中，中場保又定時定候入粒，右閘個位又填返，可以因應不同戰術換人，遲下仲買多個哥倫比亞中堅，尼馬d錢換來全方位修補。<br />\n<br />\n相反，皇馬個陣<br />\n<br />\n賓州馬 朗<br />\nIsco<br />\n卻 摩<br />\n卡斯米路<br />\n馬些路 華拉尼 拉莫斯 卡華積<br />\n拿華斯<br />\n<br />\n本身除左左閘無替補之外，全面壓制巴塞，但係賣走五大合格替補，馬里安奴、比比、摸奶、丹尼路、占屎，完全係同成個夏季各路人馬增兵情況相反。有人話主因係買唔到麥包皮，但係事實呢個陣對英超球隊已經無乜優勢。<br />\n<br />\n拖舟依家仲話乜柒都唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，究竟係乜嘢想法？"},{"pid":"8c48e33db6d9d03d6372479bc855415a847e596e","tid":521893,"uid":11914,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:00:25.000Z","msg":"拖舟落場踢未得，洗乜買人"},{"pid":"87bc9d07c2299e3ce6f37ea98efd5ec2ef079b8e","tid":521893,"uid":12360,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"拖舟贏夠 博炒掛"},{"pid":"a68affe03a1793d8126e817c78de7be0bb727e63","tid":521893,"uid":15477,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"後備就後備啦<br />\n替補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8993b7520b11cbb91f7d6de58d75d74b265e1b64","tid":521893,"uid":18279,"like":2,"dislike":41,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"a68affe03a1793d8126e817c78de7be0bb727e63","tid":521893,"uid":15477,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"後備就後備啦<br />\n替補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:10:07.000Z","msg":"我大陸仔黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485c3f59223bad758386660f5c2424bc49d26187","tid":521893,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de556f6dba2ac661a680e7dac672d843314dbb80","tid":521893,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"一堆頂級幻幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ab763a7ddf5761889647d3ebd0946572dff43c","tid":521893,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"賓施馬含得好<br />\n賣走晒所有競爭對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bb6edb8ed928aad78656a77281ba30812be488","tid":521893,"uid":993,"like":45,"dislike":17,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"坐擁歷史第一中場都叫無深度？<br />\n<br />\n世上第一防中米路，歷史最強中中摩迪卻奧斯<br />\n<br />\n西班牙歷史第一進攻中場Isco<br />\n<br />\n超越同齡小花，但比同齡C朗有唔少差距嘅阿辛斯奧<br />\n<br />\nWonderkid Cxxxxxx都棄暗投明入我皇<br />\n<br />\n仲有我皇青訓近50年最強嘅洛蘭迪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅中場都叫廢？"},{"pid":"1179586f29cd8f4f235908c0d6e7e62964f76bf3","tid":521893,"uid":63202,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過其實係我地太強<br />\n歐聯最佳中場 三個都係皇<br />\n仲有一堆頂級幻幻"},{"pid":"17952926c71b01ac535158a56d9f3a315039134d","tid":521893,"uid":4308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:20:48.000Z","msg":"覺得佢等緊今年法國仆直<br />\n換佢上任"},{"pid":"1d17e54fbef8d58cec3e7ede755d24831cdfcb1b","tid":521893,"uid":128219,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:22:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8c329fb1340aa0576cb3d1396257378a120cfd1","tid":521893,"uid":43557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>後備就後備啦<br />